dat <- read_sheet("https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16VtdtWUEtFVlWBeV2O8JhWhcqXgur8g_-PKDsBjWL2c/edit?usp=sharing")

names(dat)[2] <- "Author(s)"

# create table
n <- length(dat$Title)
datatable(dat,
  extensions = "Buttons",
  rownames = FALSE,
  filter = "top",
  options = list(
    pageLength = 100,
    order = list(0, "asc"),
    autoWidth = TRUE,
    dom = "Blfrtip",
    buttons = c("copy", "csv", "excel", "pdf", "print")
  ),
  escape = FALSE
)
